{"tid":1133704,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【淡友俠落錯車 9 年】新葵芳 9 年升值兩倍","createTime":"2019-05-01T09:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T14:48:59.000Z","uid":43146,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1d19ba66e30765c3f4c307ed0269f80c4e25ba","tid":1133704,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T09:23:18.000Z","msg":"【淡友俠落錯車 9 年】新葵芳 9 年升值兩倍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1133702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1133702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n領都售1360萬雙破頂<br />\n<br />\n鄰近的青衣區亦見搶盤。中原蔡偉明稱，青衣翠怡花園7座中層F室放盤後，即有數組客同時洽購，當中一組上車客睇好後市，見市場放盤不多，以600萬元承接該單位，以實用面積368方呎計，呎價約16,304元。<br />\n<br />\n新盤開售亦帶動二手樓成交氣氛，將軍澳日出康城屋苑被買家高追。美聯林志堅透露，領都1座右翼高層四房單位，實用面積965方呎，今年一月已開始放盤，市況轉旺後成功沽出。單位成交價1,360萬元，呎價14,093元，做價及呎價同創項目新高。"},{"pid":"837ffdca8f0c1de38033bc8c03d05053c8847421","tid":1133704,"uid":241363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:41:58.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"4206721ae878621c231112dafe6fae6fce74e9cc","tid":1133704,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"領都咁唔方便都萬4蚊尺 : O<br />\n點解唔買新樓 montara/malibu都係差唔多"},{"pid":"726f4fd1908ce4ae23422edc6055102c96d8b050","tid":1133704,"uid":19676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:10:50.000Z","msg":"廢淡唔見晒"},{"pid":"f0cbec487730aa369a9fe2bcfcd3f8ef08dde01e","tid":1133704,"uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"4206721ae878621c231112dafe6fae6fce74e9cc","tid":1133704,"uid":47883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:06:13.000Z","msg":"領都咁唔方便都萬4蚊尺 : O<br />\n點解唔買新樓 montara/malibu都係差唔多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"抽到前籌先有得買<br />\n<br />\n而家唔駛抽有得即簽既晉海要成 18k 一呎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc867125588d2a8f6634c74ea82a4e88b1311694","tid":1133704,"uid"